⁣
⭐️ ¿Cuál es la relación entre una dieta rica en plantas de calidad y la posibilidad de infectarse?⁣

⭐️ ¿Debe verse la dieta como otra capa de mitigación? ⁣
⁣
Fuente:⁣
⁣
Jordi Merino, Amit D Joshi, Long H Nguyen, Emily R Leeming, Mohsen Mazidi et all. Diet quality and risk and severity of COVID-19: a prospective cohort study. Gut, 2021; gutjnl-2021-325353 DOI: 10.1136/gutjnl-2021-325353

node.text:
I was residing outside USA when the twin towers were attacked. And although as a foreigner, it felt unreal  and painful, it was hard to grasp the whole of what New Yorkers went through. ⁣
⁣
14 years after 9/11 I moved to NY with my wife and our 4 year old. This city has given us everything we need. Education, friends, a purpose.  I’m forever indebted to this beautiful city and it is our duty to remember the courage of people during those terrible days. To pay our respects to those heroes who fought for this country and helped other during those frightening days. ⁣
⁣
The fallen New Yorkers will never be forgotten. #9/11 #neverforget 📸 by @apnews
